{"tid":2035674,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「唔好屌住睇哂先」527唔好去港島","createTime":"2020-05-26T05:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T05:40:12.000Z","uid":197235,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9b2d944beb3b978352864949f7e44a1292e6ec55","tid":2035674,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:28:55.000Z","msg":"立法會已經<span style=\"color: red;\">唔屬於香港人</span><br />\n<br />\n2019年送中條例係中共港共仲有顧忌先終止<br />\n<br />\n2020連國安法都出埋 你覺得佢地仲會理香港人？<br />\n<br />\n你527當日可以阻止 第二日 第三日 都無可能持續落去<br />\n<br />\n再講獻世派<span style=\"color: red;\">要立法可以去其他地方做</span><br />\n<br />\n佢地選主席已經<span style=\"color: red;\">「搲」爛塊面唔使再做戲</span><br />\n<br />\n你可能覺得我叫人唔好出黎<br />\n<br />\n咁<span style=\"color: red;\">你就錯</span><br />\n<br />\n我只係<span style=\"color: red;\">叫你唔好去難走難打易被捕嘅港島</span><br />\n<br />\n而係九龍 <br />\n<br />\n可能你覺得九龍同港島一樣<br />\n<br />\n但我會覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">九龍容易集人 容易走人</span><br />\n<br />\n尖咀到美孚/樂富任你走<br />\n<br />\n只要<span style=\"color: red;\">不陣地戰 互相幫助 睇住手足</span>一定比港島好<br />\n<br />\n可能你話<span style=\"color: red;\">九龍阻止唔到立法會</span><br />\n<br />\n但係實際上<span style=\"color: red;\">你港島金鐘都入唔到 </span><br />\n<br />\n依加最重要係向國際展示<span style=\"color: red;\">反抗意志</span><br />\n<br />\n只要我地有<span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭行為 </span><span style=\"color: red;\">不需介懷地方</span> 國際會知道 <br />\n<br />\n根本唔需要<span style=\"color: red;\">送羊入虎口</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">保存生命 才能長期抗爭</span><br />\n<br />\n最後祝港人有<span style=\"color: red;\">自由意志 </span>清楚真正目標<br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\">中共攬炒，港人迎戰</span>」"},{"pid":"cb8674c26aaf37876db0761ba1f3d682f7d05f08","tid":2035674,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:29:11.000Z","msg":"再開"},{"pid":"11055368ba4e7356e6e3e87a320ef4b53553d0e3","tid":2035674,"uid":197235,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:29:55.000Z","msg":"今次佢哋一早封晒路<br />\n<br />\n行人天橋都唔俾人<br />\n<br />\n要認真諗一諗去邊"},{"pid":"71626212dbc4988b769090e482ea04fde2fe0ab0","tid":2035674,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:30:07.000Z","msg":"開花又好"},{"pid":"e7b82788b2741480ef6559ae651c292d37a4acf5","tid":2035674,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:30:17.000Z","msg":"九龍又好"},{"pid":"eb99d8f53e939cf5ff66abbdb0f72da115cba3f5","tid":2035674,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:30:29.000Z","msg":"人地屋企都好"},{"pid":"087de7533f982322acd14e9646ffd10083f934ab","tid":2035674,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:31:19.000Z","msg":"「唔好屌住」527唔好去港島<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2034809\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2034809</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"942078c839d416ef8f5a820da6b69d3e3ddaa08c","tid":2035674,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6a6b44ed7b8a5e48592f48850d0c61135c4b30","tid":2035674,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:32:11.000Z","msg":"人地部署好哂<br />\n<br />\n仲有準備過上年"},{"pid":"b3bf04ebb473f8b131ab18b82189fe8e76d6194e","tid":2035674,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />